source.description: This list contains all currently ENERGY STAR certified residential clothes washers. A detailed listing of key efficiency criteria are available at https://www.energystar.gov/index.cfm?c=clotheswash.pr_crit_clothes_washers.

datasets.name: ENERGY STAR Certified Residential Clothes Washers
datasets.description: Certified models meet all ENERGY STAR requirements as listed in the Version 6.1 ENERGY STAR Program Requirements for Clothes Washers that are effective as of February 1, 2013. A detailed listing of key efficiency criteria are available at http://www.energystar.gov/index.cfm?c=clotheswash.pr_crit_clothes_washers
